{"tid":2240760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那增13人確診新型肺炎　6宗來自山東本土","createTime":"2020-10-13T01:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T02:50:49.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae95e588d39e3eccc1702ea0a5b58aefdeb8b62","tid":2240760,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554421-20201013.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554421-20201013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=9898085a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554421-20201013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=62821d34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554421-20201013.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n內地過去一日新增13人確診感染新型肺炎，其中6宗是山東的本土病例，是內地近2個月以來，再次出現本土感染病例。另外，有7宗確診個案是由境外輸入，分別來自上海、廣東、內蒙古和四川。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，山東的6宗本土確診病例，均與青島市胸科醫院有高度關聯，其中兩名患者在醫院不同樓層感染，未知感染原因，青島今日有過百班航班要取消。<br />\n<br />\n新增的17名無症狀感染者中，部分亦來自山東本土。內地累積85591人確診，4624人死亡，80729人康復出院。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>病毒黃傳染黃金周</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a302e85c0848711ac50a7bd23909be7bfc0f5afd","tid":2240760,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a828d58d272336c9e0f1c1fd538b3797eff3960b","tid":2240760,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T01:49:23.000Z","msg":"假撚到   <br />\n是但報幾單 就當報左"},{"pid":"c5b312a047005531c1dcbf5d2dacc72e69ab936e","tid":2240760,"uid":103050,"like":6,"